Package: lssdoc
Title: Generate Word Review Documents from LimeSurvey '.lss' Files
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Amal", "Tawfik", , "amal.tawfik@hesav.ch", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"), comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0006-2422-1555", ROR = "04j47fz63"))
Description: Build a professional Word ('.docx') review document from a
    LimeSurvey '.lss' export, displaying up to four languages side by side.
    The output supports human review of multilingual questionnaires by
    ethics committees, translators, and methodologists: it reproduces the
    questionnaire content faithfully and flags automatically detectable
    anomalies that do not require any AI. Processing is fully local, so no
    questionnaire is uploaded to any third-party service.
